        KEYWORDS="editors"
           SHORT="Cooledit is a full featured text editor"
cat << EOF
Cooledit is a text editor for the X Window System. It contains a
built-in Python interpreter for macro programming, and it includes a
rich set of utilities and features. It has multiple edit windows and
a beautiful, intuitive user interface that requires no tutoring to
learn to use. It can be used as a programmer's IDE and has syntax
highlighting for a large number of programming languages. It contains
an interactive graphical debugger for C/C++ programs.
EOF
